reviewText: I love the original yugioh. This series was one of my favorite childhood television shows and I'm on a mission to get the entire series. This season was pretty good.
Bought this to complete my fourth season of Yu-Gi-Oh! Great gift for any Yu-Gi-Oh! fan and really any anime lover.
Nice, pretty great, got it for my bf he loved it. All ready seen it he just wanted his own. Enjoy it.
It came in perfect working condition. Thank you
